quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Have you seen him who denies the deen
  107,2,He is the one who harshly rebuffs the orphan
  107,3,and does not urge the feeding of the poor
  107,4,So woe to those who do salat
  107,5,and are forgetful of their salat
  107,6,those who show off
  107,7,and deny help to others